  <display_name>Replace Water Heater Mixed with Thermal Storage Chilled Water</display_name>
  <description>This measure is a quick fix for GUI issue that prevents putting thermal storage on two plant loops.</description>
  <modeler_description>The model in this case used a water heater mixed as a place holder. This measure will take a string argument, and will replace the water heater with a new thermal storage chilled water object.</modeler_description>
